**/.git
**/.vs
**/.vscode
**/bin
**/obj
**/logs
**/uploads
**/tests
**/*.user
**/*.md
**/database
**/.gitignore

# ...but the AI skill guidance and the knowledge base are embedded resources
# compiled into the API (AiSkillGuidance / KbSeeder) — they MUST be in the build
# context. Re-include them after the blanket **/*.md exclusion above.
!src/Lilia.Api/AiSkills/*.md
!src/Lilia.Api/AiSkills/**/*.md
!src/Lilia.Api/Kb/*.md
!src/Lilia.Api/Kb/**/*.md
